      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 max-w-3xl font-medium leading-relaxed mb-8">
        AI builders make money from lock-in, not features. <span class="text-red-600 font-black">127 hours</span> of testing reveals what they don't tell you.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <div class="px-5 py-3 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur rounded-lg border-2 border-rose-200">
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-rose-600">87</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 font-semibold mt-1">Migration Attempts</div>
        </div>
        <div class="px-5 py-3 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur rounded-lg border-2 border-rose-200">
