      <div class="bg-red-50 border-[3px] border-red-400 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-center text-red-900 font-black text-lg">
          This article will upset some AI builder founders. Good.
          <br><span class="text-sm font-normal mt-2 block">Someone needs to say it.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
