            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">•</span>
              <span><strong>Framer:</strong> React export (requires dev work). Free plan available for testing.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">•</span>
              <span><strong>10Web:</strong> WordPress export (requires WordPress hosting). Good if you know WordPress.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">•</span>
              <span><strong>Static site generators (Hugo, Astro):</strong> Open source, real code ownership. Tradeoff: requires technical skill.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">Decision Framework</h3>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6">
              <h4 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">If Lock-In Matters to You:</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                <li>• Choose CodeDesign.ai (real code export)</li>
                <li>• Or choose static site generators (full ownership)</li>
                <li>• Accept that AI builders are rental, not ownership</li>
                <li>• Plan for long-term costs: 3 years of payments</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6">
              <h4 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">If Speed Matters More Than Ownership:</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                <li>• Accept the lock-in tradeoff</li>
                <li>• Choose Framer or Durable (fastest AI builders)</li>
                <li>• Budget for 3+ years of monthly fees</li>
                <li>• Don't expect to export later—plan to stay or rebuild</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- FINAL VERDICT -->
      <section class="bg-gray-900 p-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6">The Brutal Truth</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
          AI website builders aren't villains. They offer legitimate value: speed, ease of use, beautiful templates. The lock-in tactics are the business model that makes those features possible.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
          But you should enter with eyes open. You're not buying software. You're renting infrastructure. If you stop paying, your business disappears. That's the deal.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-[#F5521A] p-8 rounded-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <p class="text-white text-lg mb-6">
            <strong>The right choice depends on your priorities:</strong>
          </p>
          <div class="text-left space-y-3 text-white">
            <p>✓ <strong>Need it fast and don't care about ownership?</strong> Framer or Durable.</p>
            <p>✓ <strong>Want to own your code?</strong> CodeDesign.ai or build from scratch.</p>
            <p>✓ <strong>Building a long-term brand?</strong> Consider WordPress or custom development.</p>
            <p>✓ <strong>Testing an idea?</strong> Free AI builder, then migrate if successful.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12">
          <a href="/guides/how-to-choose" class="inline-block bg-white text-gray-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-black text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
            Decision Framework: Choose the Right Builder →
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- FAQ Section -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-1 h-10 bg-rose-600"></div>
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-50 to-red-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-rose-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">What is the lock-in trap with AI website builders?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
