            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Can I export my website from AI builders?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              <strong class="text-rose-600">Depends on the builder.</strong> No export at all: Durable, Mixo, Wix (site disappears if you stop paying). Useless export: Framer (React code requires build tools - less than 5% ever actually use it), Wix (XML format no other tool reads). Partial export: Webflow (HTML/CSS export but missing CMS functionality). Real export: CodeDesign.ai (clean HTML/CSS you can deploy), 10Web (WordPress export if you have WordPress hosting). The reality: 'code export' is mostly marketing. Internally, Framer knows less than 5% of users export. Most export to GitHub, look at React code, realize they can't deploy, and go back to paying.
            </p>
